   ```

5. **Focus on HIGH-LEVERAGE insights:**
   - Insights that prevent entire classes of bugs
   - Patterns that save significant tokens/time
   - Platform/tool behaviors not documented elsewhere

6. **DO NOT record:**
   - One-off typos or obvious mistakes
   - Things already caught by compiler/linter
   - Issues specific to this iteration only

