```json
{"timestamp":"2026-02-08T07:06:26Z","phase":["PLAN"],"severity":"IMPORTANT","problem":"Spec ordering from task.md checklist not preserved, causing unintended reordering","impact":["Specs execute in wrong order","User expectations violated"],"antipattern":["Falling back to directory sorting without checking task.md"],"solution":["Always preserve ordering from task.md checklist entries","Only fall back to directory sorting if no checklist entries found"],"context":"When bootstrapping specs, check task.md first"}
```

